{"tid":1389789,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職工盟稱暫有26個工會響應下周一罷工行動","createTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:58:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"70cb3735805f3465a6c8a333adcc11e9c1e73672","tid":1389789,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471545-20190731.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471545-20190731.htm&d=z0v15oAQEaIuorZt047Ij2DcYOQIx6XO0JIcXsozN2c%3D&h=234ae3ea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1471545-20190731.htm&h=f171b822\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1471545-20190731.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n職工盟主席吳敏兒說，現時有26個工會表示會響應下星期一的罷工行動，預料對公私營機構運作將造成不便。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒出席一個電台節目後表示，不合作運動已擴展至不同層面，如果政府繼續不回應，第3次罷工將會升級行動。<br />\n<br />\n她表示，下星期一的罷工是不上班的罷工，參與的僱員需通知僱主，《基本法》賦予員工享有罷工權利，只要僱員有以口頭或書面通知僱主，僱主在罷工後不能留難僱員。<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒說，僱主大多只會扣減罷工僱員的一日薪金，如果僱員在罷工後，懷疑受到不合理的對待，可通知工會。"},{"pid":"6028633e624c8edc83abed4fb40a26d2298d4cab","tid":1389789,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:46:19.000Z","msg":"入黎睇下一齊呼籲罷工 幫手推<br />\n<br />\n有人為你衝，你肯唔肯為佢唔返工？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1389755\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1389755</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5333feccad842d57f5a2fec57c929b165e90caba","tid":1389789,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:47:10.000Z","msg":"基本法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e59932dce778b0281af93cb4167abbce541aa92","tid":1389789,"uid":35886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T03:48:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11d94811ec92d9604d20999f7d975f378097f4f0","tid":1389789,"uid":45877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,